# Screenshot Collection Plan — Hospital Management System

## Overview

Systematically capture screenshots of **every page** in the hospital management system, organized by access level and role. All screenshots saved to:

```
d:\projects\hospital-management-system\web\screenshot-each-page\
```

**Frontend URL:** `http://localhost:3000`
**Backend API:** `http://localhost:8081/api/v1`

---

## Prerequisites

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Both backend and frontend must be running before starting.

1. **Backend** — `cd backend && .\run.ps1` (Spring Boot on port 8081)
2. **Frontend** — `cd web && npm run dev` (Next.js on port 3000)
3. **Seed data** — auto-loaded on first backend boot

---

