## Execution Method

Use **Chrome browser** via `browser_subagent` and `chrome-devtools` MCP:

1. Navigate to each URL
2. Wait for page load
3. Take full-page screenshot → save to `d:\projects\hospital-management-system\web\screenshot-each-page\{name}.png`
4. For authenticated pages: login once per role session, capture all accessible pages, then logout
5. Handle dynamic pages (e.g., `/staff/doctor/[id]`) using known seed data IDs

> [!NOTE]
> Some pages with dynamic `[id]` params may show "not found" if no matching record exists. We'll use seed data IDs where available.
